commit.message: Add Slovak translation

Fix locale-related segfault.

Closes: http://code.google.com/p/grun/issues/detail?id=1
Use g_strjoinv for concatenating cmdline in the case of running a command directly
Call to g_strjoinv in --preload arg handling. Closes Debian #300296.
Update config.{guess,sub} files from recent autotools
Swedish translation by Daniel Nylander, from Debian bug #348254.
Source line numbering and typo fixes in existing po files
Remove unused vars

Remove all uses of strsep, and replace them by g_strsplit

strsep's interface is rather ugly, and forced the code to jump thru hoops
to save references to ponters for later freeing, specially when all we cared
about was the first element from the split.

Install gassoc and consfile to SYSCONFDIR.

Since these files are customizable by the sysadmin, they are better
installed to sysconfdir.

Reorganize a bit Makefile.am, but the only real change is the location
of the files.

Record this change in the Changelog. This is the real 0.9.3 release. Lucky
me had not tagged anything in svn or uploaded a tarball yet.
Record release of 0.9.3
Ensure XTERM is only used when TESTFILE is defined.
Store the actual config.* files, and not just symlinks
Do not try to distribute removed INSTALL.Win file
Updated po files. No important changes.
Another file created on build
Modernize a bit the associations file

Use a dynamic GTK layout for the window widgets.

Using the 'fixed' layout for widgets causes them to be unable to
adjust to changes in text size, such as that caused by using different
fonts, or by translations.

Closes Debian bug #445466.

Clean up logic in startApp and isFileExec.

Rework the logic of the two mentioned functions to avoid such deep nesting of
if/elses. Avoid conditionaly compiled code inside startApp. Now, the only code
protected by #defines is inside two well demarcated functions.

Debian fixes and improvements to autocompletion.

I don't understand these patches yet, but since they are
working in the Debian version, I have no reason to doubt them :).
Move cursor before selecting regions
Ignore compiled program and TAGS file in VC
Clean up use of TESTFILE define
The quotes around DATADIR must be provided by the define

Fix window icon setting.
Make the icon data be in .rodata section.
Include <locale.h>.
Use DATADIR for the location of data files
main must return int
Remove WIN32 port code
Add function prototypes
